        public static com.google.common.collect.ImmutableMap<BuildTarget,NativeLinkable> getNativeLinkableRoots(Iterable<? extends BuildRule> from,
                                                                                                        com.google.common.base.Predicate<Object> traverse)
        Find all NativeLinkable transitive roots reachable from the given BuildRules.
        Parameters:
        from - the starting set of BuildRules to begin the search from.
        traverse - a Predicate determining acceptable dependencies to traverse when searching for NativeLinkables.
        Returns:
        all the roots found as a map from BuildTarget to NativeLinkable.

        linkStyle - how dependencies should be linked, if their preferred_linkage is NativeLinkable.Linkage.ANY.
